Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.67,Screen2,,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZLanTingYuan-B-GBK\frz270\bord0\shad2\4c&H9F9F9F&\pos(706.667,245.333)}利索地搬运建材
